x4freetext: No error analysis given. On the basis of
similar experiment by same author (Nucl. Phys.54,17),
the compiler assumes the errors to be mainly
statistical,and the energy resolution of the incoming
neutrons to be of 0.1 MeV except for Rh-103, for which
(n,a) reactions on oxygen of the counters and
silicium of the E-counter cause the main background.
